Library/Family: Library of Automation Framework Author: Siemens Digital Industry Tested with: S7-PLCSIM Advanced 6.0 Engineering: TIA Portal V19 Restrictions: --- Requirements: --- ------------------------------------------------------------------------------ Change log table: Version | Date | Expert in charge | Changes applied ---------|------------|------------------------|------------------------------ 01.01.00 | 21.06.2024 | SIMATIC Systems Support | First released version 01.02.00 | 30.09.2024 | SIMATIC Systems Support | Block information properties updated and optimized code

The LAF_MapUnitStatusToSequence function block is used to connect the unit status signals to the sequencer interface. If the active Unit Mode is Manual, the HMI interface signals are used to control the sequence. The block should be adapted if another Unit Control Manager is used.
Set the Sequencer in Automatic Mode.
Set the Sequencer in Manual Mode.
Set the Sequencer and Job Management in Manual Control
Stop the Sequence and set it to the idle step in resetting/aborting/stopping OMAC state.
